===Adjective===
''apocryphal''

# of dubious veracity

2 of doubtful authenticity

3 like the nature of an urban legend/myth (i.e. there is nothing fantasy-like or unreal about it so it could be true, but based on factors like it's incredulous nature it probably is false.)
